   "source": "<ROUTINE V-DIAGNOSE ()\n         <COND (<AND <NOT ,DREAMING>\n\t\t     <G? ,MEET-COUNTER 7>>\n\t \t<SETG AWAITING-REPLY 9>\n\t\t<ENABLE <QUEUE I-REPLY 2>>\n\t\t<TELL \n\"Are you really so heartless as to think of your own well-being at a time\nlike this?\" CR>)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<TELL \"You're \">\n\t\t<COND (<FSET? ,BANANA ,RMUNGBIT>\n\t\t       <TELL \"still \">)>\n\t\t<TELL \"famished.\" CR>)>>"
