   "endLine": 386,
   "source": "<ROUTINE V-ASK-ABOUT ()\n\t <COND (<PRSO? ,ME>\n\t\t<PERFORM ,V?TELL ,ME>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       ;(<FSET? ,PRSO ,ACTORBIT>\n\t\t<SETG WINNER ,PRSO>\n\t\t<PERFORM ,V?TELL-ABOUT ,ME ,PRSI>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)\n\t       (<FSET? ,PRSO ,ACTORBIT>\n\t\t<TELL \"A long silence tells you that\">\n\t\t<ARTICLE ,PRSO T>\n\t\t<TELL \" isn't interested in talking about\">\n\t\t<COND (<IN? ,PRSI ,ROOMS>\n\t\t       <TELL \" that\">)\n\t\t      (T\n\t\t       <ARTICLE ,PRSI T>)>\n\t\t<TELL ,PERIOD>)\n\t       (T\n\t\t<PERFORM ,V?TELL ,PRSO>\n\t\t<RTRUE>)>>"
