   "source": "<ROUTINE HERM-DESC (\"OPTIONAL\" X)\n\t <SET P-IT-OBJECT ,ANDREW>\n\t <TELL \n\"Andrew Jenny is the attraction of this sideshow. He appears standoffish,\nshe's looking bored.\">>"
